quote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當大家磨合到又會冇左火花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c003243cb14772c1f3d6530016a7669b546aa7","tid":225932,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:37:22.000Z","msg":"通常都係上一代<br />\n以前戀愛單純啲"},{"pid":"b0af7aa4f818ed8827b2d81a14f9687d72a9b4ae","tid":225932,"uid":10326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我就冇咁嘅福份<br />\n但聽過兩個case<br />\n一個中學呀sir 同佢老婆中三拍到結婚<br />\n中間冇分開過<br />\n另一個係我親戚 又係中三拍<br />\n女嘅老豆棒打鴛鴦就分開咗<br />\n幾年前朋友聚會撞返再拍拖拉埋天窗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個呀sir係咪好好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你親戚係緣份</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個呀sir係超級好人<br />\n<br />\n親戚係80後 都唔算好上一代嘅<br />\n<br />\n有對中學師弟妹都係初戀拍到而家7年了<br />\n希望佢地結得成婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己冇就好想睇人地有 覺得世界冇咁絕望"},{"pid":"eb2941b9a6115205a1695fa73ab4ab6896e8bdd4","tid":225932,"uid":10326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我就冇咁嘅福份<br />\n但聽過兩個case<br />\n一個中學呀sir 同佢老婆中三拍到結婚<br />\n中間冇分開過<br />\n另一個係我親戚 又係中三拍<br />\n女嘅老豆棒打鴛鴦就分開咗<br />\n幾年前朋友聚會撞返再拍拖拉埋天窗</blockquote><br />\n以前就有可能<br />\n呢個年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難啲囉<br />\n我一開始都有呢種天真諗法，想同女朋友一齊改進，但啲唔係一個人堅持就有用，比你咁啱大家都咁堅持咪可以走到尾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當大家磨合到又會冇左火花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱呀 磨合咗又會俾班港女話似屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1783dcacc151e068a47c3276d8144ee311a9946","tid":225932,"uid":89804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re